## Use Case Description

### Actors
- **User** - Authenticated user of the app
- **System** - WorkManager background service

### Use Cases

#### Authentication
| Use Case | Description |
|----------|-------------|
| Sign In | Authenticate with Google Firebase Auth |
| Sign Out | Sign out of the account |

#### CRUD Operations
| Use Case | Description |
|----------|-------------|
| Add Receipt | Create a new receipt entry |
| Add Warranty | Create a new warranty entry |
| Edit Item | Modify existing receipt/warranty |
| View Item Details | See full details of an item |
| Delete Item | Remove item from storage |

#### Browse & View
| Use Case | Description |
|----------|-------------|
| Search Items | Search by title, company, notes |
| Filter Items | Filter by type, category, status |
| View Dashboard | See overview and quick stats |
| View Statistics | View detailed counts and charts |

#### Sync & Export
| Use Case | Description |
|----------|-------------|
| Manual Sync | Trigger full sync manually |
| Auto Sync | Automatic sync on item save |
| Export to CSV | Export all data to CSV file |

#### Reminders
| Use Case | Description |
|----------|-------------|
| Schedule Reminder | Set warranty expiry reminder |
| Cancel Reminder | Remove scheduled reminder |
| Receive Notification | Get notification when triggered |

#### Image Handling
| Use Case | Description |
|----------|-------------|
| Upload Image | Attach image to receipt/warranty |
| View Image | View attached image |
